>>> [ 31] 2F_04.01.Zefiro-Europe.TRS.772
    [ 32] Description
    [ 33] It shall be possible to select the country which the train will be operated in from the IDU. Possible counties are:
    [ 34] - Italy, Austria, Belgium, France, Germany, Netherlands, Spain and Switzerland.
    [ 35] The country selection shall be used for country specific configurations such as:
    [ 36] - selection of wide or narrow pantograph
    [ 37] - levels of line voltage supervision
    [ 38] - levels of line current harmonics.
