>>> [ 13] 2F_04.01.Zefiro-
    [ 14] Europe.CONCEPT.1002
    [ 15] In a multiple coupled train:
    [ 16] If pantograph 1 is selected to raise
    [ 17] then the following actions shall be
    [ 18] performed in priority order:
    [ 19] 1) If both front pantographs are not ok
    [ 20] then no pantograph shall be raised
    [ 21] and an event shall be set for driver
